頓","Riccarton Castle, Paisley, Renfrew, Scotland":"蘇格蘭雷福福爾佩斯利","Ayrshire, Scotland":"英國蘇格蘭艾斯爾","lifeSummary":"當Richard Wallace於1117年出生在蘇格蘭艾斯爾時，他的父親Aymer de Wallace27歲，母親Lady Eimerus de Wallense22歲。他於1142年與Emma de Grainsby在蘇格蘭米德洛迪安利卡頓結婚。他們至少是1個兒子的父母。他去世於1180年在英國蘇格蘭艾斯爾享年63歲。"},"zh-hans":{"1117–1180":"1117年–1180年","1124–1206":"1124年–1206年","1143–1214":"1143年–1214年","1090–1181":"1090年–1181年","1095–Female":"1095年–殁","1206":"1206年","1117":"1117年","1090":"1090年","1115":"1115年","1214":"1214年","1124":"1124年","1143":"1143年","1142":"1142年","1095":"1095年","1181":"1181年","1180":"1180年","Riccarton, Midlothian, Scotland":"苏格兰米德洛迪安利卡頓","Riccarton, Ayrshire, Scotland":"苏格兰艾斯爾利卡頓","Riccarton Castle, Paisley, Renfrew, Scotland":"苏格兰雷福福爾佩斯利","Ayrshire, Scotland":"英国苏格兰艾斯爾","lifeSummary":"当Richard Wallace于1117年出生在苏格兰艾斯爾时，他的父亲Aymer de Wallace27岁，母亲Lady Eimerus de Wallense22岁。他于1142年与Emma de Grainsby在苏格兰米德洛迪安利卡頓结婚。他们至少是1个儿子的父母。他去世于1180年在英国苏格兰艾斯爾享年63岁。"},"hr":{"1117–1180":"1117.–1180.","1124–1206":"1124–1206","1143–1214":"1143.–1214","1090–1181":"1090–1181","1095–Female":"1095–preminula","1206":"1206","1117":"1117.","1090":"1090","1115":"1115.","1214":"1214","1124":"1124","1143":"1143.","1142":"1142.","1095":"1095","1181":"1181","1180":"1180.","Riccarton, Midlothian, Scotland":"Riccarton, Midlothian, Scotland","Riccarton, Ayrshire, Scotland":"Riccarton, Ayrshire, Scotland","Riccarton Castle, Paisley, Renfrew, Scotland":"Paisley, Renfrewshire, Scotland","Ayrshire, Scotland":"Ayrshire, Škotska, United Kingdom"},"cs":{"1117–1180":"1117–1180","1124–1206":"1124–1206","1143–1214":"1143–1214","1090–1181":"1090–1181","1095–Female":"1095–Zesnulá","1206":"1206","1117":"1117","1090":"1090","1115":"1115","1214":"1214","1124":"1124","1143":"1143","1142":"1142","1095":"1095","1181":"1181","1180":"1180","Riccarton, Midlothian, Scotland":"Riccarton, Midlothian, Scotland","Riccarton, Ayrshire, Scotland":"Riccarton, Ayrshire, Scotland","Riccarton Castle, Paisley, Renfrew, Scotland":"Paisley, Renfrewshire, S